## Section 5: Typography Token System

### 5.1 Overview

The SabPaisa COB typography system uses **Inter** as the primary font family with a complete scale of sizes, weights, line heights, and letter spacing values.

**Font Stack**:
- **Heading**: `Inter, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', sans-serif`
- **Body**: `Inter, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', sans-serif`
- **Monospace**: `source-code-pro, Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, 'Courier New', monospace`

**Future Enhancement**: When licenses are acquired:
- Heading Font → `Neusharp Bold`
- Body Font → `Sofia Pro`

---

### 5.2 Font Size Scale

| Name | Rem | Pixels | Tailwind | Line Height (Default) | Usage Context |
|------|-----|--------|----------|----------------------|---------------|
| **xs** | 0.75rem | 12px | `text-xs` | 1rem (16px) | Helper text, captions, meta info |
| **sm** | 0.875rem | 14px | `text-sm` | 1.25rem (20px) | Small text, labels, compact UIs |
| **base** | 1rem | 16px | `text-base` | 1.5rem (24px) | **Body text (DEFAULT)** |
| **lg** | 1.125rem | 18px | `text-lg` | 1.75rem (28px) | Large body text, emphasis |
| **xl** | 1.25rem | 20px | `text-xl` | 1.75rem (28px) | H5, small headings |
| **2xl** | 1.5rem | 24px | `text-2xl` | 2rem (32px) | **H4**, card headers |
| **3xl** | 1.875rem | 30px | `text-3xl` | 2.25rem (36px) | **H3**, section titles |
| **4xl** | 2.25rem | 36px | `text-4xl` | 2.5rem (40px) | **H2**, page titles |
| **5xl** | 3rem | 48px | `text-5xl` | 3rem (48px) | **H1**, hero headings |

---

### 5.3 Font Weight Scale

| Name | Weight | Tailwind | Usage |
|------|--------|----------|-------|
| **normal** | 400 | `font-normal` | Body text, default weight |
| **medium** | 500 | `font-medium` | Emphasis, buttons, labels |
| **semibold** | 600 | `font-semibold` | Subheadings, strong emphasis |
| **bold** | 700 | `font-bold` | Headings, strong emphasis |
| **extrabold** | 800 | `font-extrabold` | Display text, hero headings |

---

### 5.4 Line Height Scale

| Name | Value | Tailwind | Usage |
|------|-------|----------|-------|
| **none** | 1 | `leading-none` | Tight line height, logos |
| **tight** | 1.25 | `leading-tight` | Tight spacing, headings |
| **snug** | 1.375 | `leading-snug` | Snug spacing, subheadings |
| **normal** | 1.5 | `leading-normal` | **Normal spacing (DEFAULT)** |
| **relaxed** | 1.625 | `leading-relaxed` | Relaxed spacing, long-form text |
| **loose** | 2 | `leading-loose` | Loose spacing, poetry, special cases |

---

### 5.5 Letter Spacing Scale

| Name | Value | Tailwind | Usage |
|------|-------|----------|-------|
| **tighter** | -0.05em | `tracking-tighter` | Very tight tracking |
| **tight** | -0.025em | `tracking-tight` | Tight tracking, headings |
| **normal** | 0em | `tracking-normal` | **Normal tracking (DEFAULT)** |
| **wide** | 0.025em | `tracking-wide` | Wide tracking, labels |
| **wider** | 0.05em | `tracking-wider` | Wider tracking, uppercase |
| **widest** | 0.1em | `tracking-widest` | Widest tracking, all-caps |

---

### 5.6 Typography Utility Classes

Defined in `src/index.css`:

```css
/* Headings */
.heading-1 {
  @apply text-5xl font-bold font-heading leading-tight;
}

.heading-2 {
  @apply text-4xl font-bold font-heading leading-tight;
}

.heading-3 {
  @apply text-3xl font-semibold font-heading leading-snug;
}

.heading-4 {
  @apply text-2xl font-semibold font-heading leading-snug;
}

.heading-5 {
  @apply text-xl font-medium font-heading leading-normal;
}

.heading-6 {
  @apply text-lg font-medium font-heading leading-normal;
}

/* Body Text */
.body-large {
  @apply text-lg font-normal font-body leading-relaxed;
}

.body-base {
  @apply text-base font-normal font-body leading-normal;
}

.body-small {
  @apply text-sm font-normal font-body leading-normal;
}

/* Special Text */
.caption {
  @apply text-xs font-normal font-body leading-normal tracking-wide;
}

.label {
  @apply text-sm font-medium font-body leading-normal uppercase tracking-wide;
}

/* Code */
.code-inline {
  @apply font-mono text-sm bg-neutral-100 dark:bg-neutral-800 px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded;
}

.code-block {
  @apply font-mono text-sm bg-neutral-100 dark:bg-neutral-800 p-4 rounded-lg overflow-x-auto;
}

/* Text Modifiers */
.text-emphasis {
  @apply font-semibold;
}

.text-subtle {
  @apply text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-400;
}

.link {
  @apply text-primary-600 hover:text-primary-700 underline transition-colors;
}
```

**Usage Example**:
```tsx
<h1 className="heading-1">Complete Your KYC</h1>
<h2 className="heading-2">Business Information</h2>
<p className="body-base">Enter your business details below.</p>
<label className="label">PAN Number</label>
<p className="caption">Format: ABCDE1234F</p>
<code className="code-inline">TXN20250115000123</code>
```

